{"tid":762664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳國泰航空宣布裁員 部分海外員工已收到通知","createTime":"2018-07-31T13:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T04:20:34.000Z","uid":20058,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75d3667984d4ed62ef02a635be5ee03fceca5c3a","tid":762664,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港國泰航空去年進行人事重組，共裁員600名員工。今有媒體報導，國泰航空再度進行整頓計畫，預計對後勤部門大裁員，部分員工已收到裁員通知。<br />\n據港媒《南華早報》報導，消息人士透露，國泰航空對員工發放一份通告，將對海外後勤業務人員進行人事重組，包含負責銷售、營銷、貨運、機場營運等相關業務的員工都會受影響，消息人士更稱，部分員工已收到裁員通知。<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，國泰航空表示，的確有向海外員工發放通告，人事重組作業會這幾個月內持續進行，不過並未透露發放通告的業務地點為何，據悉，國泰在香港以外，有100個後勤業務地點，約有7600名員工，其中以澳洲、美國、英國的人數佔最多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2504743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504743&d=wVRTPiE%2BbZQs9cg6q3yQ5DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f483ca60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504743&h=ce666aab\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2504743</a>"},{"pid":"18fe4e32b152388d9b6c47b502ddf5964b89b016","tid":762664,"uid":66825,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"唉 收到信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c1457b047acc2286b57a4cec6a47f686f142fc","tid":762664,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18fe4e32b152388d9b6c47b502ddf5964b89b016","tid":762664,"uid":66825,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"唉 收到信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"你做台灣呀？"},{"pid":"c21f3f24e8ed147648815b30f735c0747bb35037","tid":762664,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"大柴做柒自己<img src=\"/assets